 yıl ile cari yıl üretimimi karşılaştır.\\\" üretim tarafıyla ilgilenen kullanıcılar ve üst yönetim tarafından sık sorulur.\",\"En fazla üretim yapan 10 acenteyi / Akdeniz bölgesinde en fazla üretim yapan 10 acente / xxx no'lu acentenin en yüksek prime sahip ilk 10 müşterisini getir sık sorulan sorular arasındadır.\",\"No direct PII markers inferred from Excel metadata.\",\"Apply selective date filters for production reporting queries.\",\"Prefer key-based joins observed in workbook join definitions.\",\"Contains customer-identifying fields; apply least-privilege and masking in broad extracts.\",\"PII columns restricted: MUSTERI_ADI, MUSTERI_NUMARASI, MUSTERI_SOYADI\"],\"mandatory_rules\":[\"REPORT_PERIOD = :report_period\"],\"retrieval_debug\":{\"selected_count\":20,\"total_documents\":20,\"effective_top_k\":200,\"min_score_threshold\":0.005,\"metadata_source\":\"C:\\\\Users\\\\ky4642\\\\talk-to-your-data-v0\\\\metadata\\\\agents\\\\metadata_vectored_uretim.json\"}}\n\nSQL_CANDIDATES:\noption_1:\nSQL: SELECT \n  ppo.POLICE_NO,\n  pb.BRANS_KODU,\n  fpp.BRUT_PRIM_TL AS PRIM_TL\nFROM \n  AS_DWH.POL_POLICE_OZET ppo\nJOIN AS_DWH.FACT_POL_POLICE_EK fpp ON ppo.POLICE_ID = fpp.POLICE_ID\nJOIN AS_DWH.POL_POLICE_KIRILIM ppk ON ppo.POLICE_ID = ppk.POLICE_ID\nJOIN AS_DWH.POL_BRANS pb ON ppk.BRANS_ID = pb.BRANS_ID\nWHERE \n  TO_CHAR(ppo.TANZIM_TARIH_ID) BETWEEN '20250101' AND '20251231'\n  AND ppo.REPORT_PERIOD = :report_period\nFETCH FIRST 200 ROWS ONLY\nEXPLANATION: Question answered: What are the police numbers, branch codes, and gross premium amounts (in Turkish Lira) for policies issued between January 1, 2025, and December 31, 2025, filtered by a specific report period?\n\nTables used: \n- AS_DWH.POL_POLICE_OZET (policy summary)\n- AS_DWH.FACT_POL_POLICE_EK (policy premium facts)\n- AS_DWH.POL_POLICE_KIRILIM (policy breakdown)\n- AS_DWH.POL_BRANS (branch codes)\n\nFilters: \n- Policies with a formulation date between January 1, 2025, and December 31, 2025.\n- A specific report period (`:report_period`) is applied.\n\nGrouping/measures: \n- No grouping or aggregation is performed. The query simply retrieves individual policy records.\n\nExpected output columns: \n- POLICE_NO (policy number)\n- BRANS_KODU (branch code)\n- PRIM_TL (gross premium in Turkish Lira)\n\nAssumptions: \n- The `:report_period` parameter is provided externally.\n- The date filter (`TO_CHAR(ppo.TANZIM_TARIH_ID)`) refers to the formulation date of the policy.\n- The query is likely used to extract a sample of policy data for reporting or analysis purposes.\n\noption_2:\nSQL: SELECT \n  ppo.POLICE_NO,\n  pb.BRANS_KODU,\n  fppa.VOP_TL AS PRIM_TL\nFROM \n  AS_DWH.POL_POLICE_OZET ppo\nJOIN AS_DWH.FACT_POL_POLICE_TEM_ASSET fppa ON ppo.POLICE_ID = fppa.POLICE_ID\nJOIN AS_DWH.POL_POLICE_KIRILIM ppk ON ppo.POLICE_ID = ppk.POLICE_ID\nJOIN AS_DWH.POL_BRANS pb ON ppk.BRANS_ID = pb.BRANS_ID\nWHERE \n  TO_CHAR(ppo.TANZIM_TARIH_ID) BETWEEN '20250101' AND '20251231'\n  AND ppo.REPORT_PERIOD = :report_period\nFETCH FIRST 200 ROWS ONLY\nEXPLANATION: Question answered: What are the police numbers, branch codes, and premium amounts (in TL) for policies issued between January 1, 2025, and December 31, 2025, filtered by a specific report period?\n\nTables used: \n- AS_DWH.POL_POLICE_OZET (policy summary)\n- AS_DWH.FACT_POL_POLICE_TEM_ASSET (policy asset facts)\n- AS_DWH.POL_POLICE_KIRILIM (policy breakdown)\n- AS_DWH.POL_BRANS (branch codes)\n\nFilters: \n- Policies with a formulation date between January 1, 2025, and December 31, 2025.\n- A specific report period (`REPORT_PERIOD = :report_period`).\n\nGrouping/measures: \n- No grouping or aggregation is applied. The query simply retrieves individual policy records.\n\nExpected output columns: \n- POLICE_NO (policy number)\n- BRANS_KODU (branch code)\n- PRIM_TL (premium amount in Turkish Lira)\n\nAssumptions: \n- The `REPORT_PERIOD` is a parameter used to filter data according to a specific reporting timeframe.\n- The `VOP_TL` column represents the premium amount in Turkish Lira.\n- The query is likely used to extract a sample of policy records for analysis or reporting purposes.\n\noption_3:\nSQL: SELECT \n  ppo.POLICE_NO,\n  pb.BRANS_KODU,\n  fpp.BRUT_PRIM_TL AS PRIM_TL\nFROM \n  AS_DWH.POL_POLICE_OZET ppo\nJOIN AS_DWH.FACT_POL_POLICE_EK fpp ON ppo.POLICE_ID = fpp.POLICE_ID\nJOIN AS_DWH.POL_POLICE_KIRILIM ppk ON ppo.POLICE_ID = ppk.POLICE_ID\nJOIN AS_DWH.POL_BRANS pb ON ppk.BRANS_ID = pb.BRANS_ID\nWHERE \n  TO_CHAR(ppo.TANZIM_TARIH_ID) BETWEEN '20250101' AND '20251231'\n  AND ppo.REPORT_PERIOD = :report_period\nGROUP BY \n  ppo.POLICE_NO,\n  pb.BRANS_KODU,\n  fpp.BRUT_PRIM_TL\nFETCH FIRST 200 ROWS ONLY\nEXPLANATION: Question answered: What are the police numbers, branch codes, and gross premium amounts (in Turkish Lira) for policies issued in 2025, filtered by a specific report period, limited to the first 200 rows?\n\nTables used: \n- AS_DWH.POL_POLICE_OZET (policy summary)\n- AS_DWH.FACT_POL_POLICE_EK (policy additional facts)\n- AS_DWH.POL_POLICE_KIRILIM (policy breakdown)\n- AS_DWH.POL_BRANS (branch codes)\n\nFilters: \n- Policies with a formulation date between January 1, 2025, and December 31, 2025.\n- A specific report period (`:report_period`) is selected.\n\nGrouping/measures: \n- Grouped by police number, branch code, and gross premium amount.\n\nExpected output columns: \n- Police number (`POLICE_NO`)\n- Branch code (`BRANS_KODU`)\n- Gross premium in Turkish Lira (`PRIM_TL`)\n\nAssumptions: \n- The `:report_period` parameter is provided externally.\n- The query is intended to retrieve a limited sample (200 rows) for analysis or reporting purposes.\n- The joins are based on shared policy IDs and branch relationships as defined in the metadata."}
