ma yapılmalı.\",\"Üretim raporlarında genel olarak geçen sene ile kıyaslama yapılır. Örneğin \\\"Geçen yıl ile cari yıl üretimimi karşılaştır.\\\" üretim tarafıyla ilgilenen kullanıcılar ve üst yönetim tarafından sık sorulur.\",\"En fazla üretim yapan 10 acenteyi / Akdeniz bölgesinde en fazla üretim yapan 10 acente / xxx no'lu acentenin en yüksek prime sahip ilk 10 müşterisini getir sık sorulan sorular arasındadır.\",\"Contains customer-identifying fields; apply least-privilege and masking in broad extracts.\",\"PII columns restricted: MUSTERI_ADI, MUSTERI_NUMARASI, MUSTERI_SOYADI\"],\"mandatory_rules\":[\"{'month': '202512'}\"],\"runtime_mandatory_rules\":[],\"retrieval_debug\":{\"selected_count\":20,\"total_documents\":20,\"effective_top_k\":500,\"min_score_threshold\":0.005,\"metadata_source\":\"C:\\\\Users\\\\ky4642\\\\talk-to-your-data-v0\\\\metadata\\\\agents\\\\metadata_vectored_uretim.json\"}}\n\nSQL_CANDIDATES:\noption_1:\nSQL: SELECT SUM(fpp.BRUT_PRIM_TL) AS prim_üretim_tutarı FROM AS_DWH.FACT_POL_POLICE_EK fpp JOIN AS_DWH.POL_POLICE_OZET ppo ON fpp.KAYNAK_SISTEM_ID = ppo.KAYNAK_SISTEM_ID AND fpp.POLICE_ID = ppo.POLICE_ID JOIN AS_DWH.GNL_TARIH gt ON ppo.TANZIM_TARIH_ID = gt.TARIH_ID WHERE TO_CHAR(gt.TARIH) = '202512' FETCH FIRST 200 ROWS ONLY\nEXPLANATION: Question answered: What is the total production value (BRUT_PRIM_TL) for policies with an additional policy date of December 2025?\n\nTables used: AS_DWH.FACT_POL_POLICE_EK, AS_DWH.POL_POLICE_OZET, AS_DWH.GNL_TARIH\n\nFilters: Only records where the additional policy date (TANZIM_TARIH_ID) corresponds to December 2025.\n\nGrouping/measures: Summing the BRUT_PRIM_TL column to calculate the total production value.\n\nExpected output columns: prim_üretim_tutarı (total production value in Turkish Lira)\n\nAssumptions: \n- The query assumes that the additional policy date (ek tanzim tarihi) is the correct basis for production reporting in this context.\n- The date filter is applied via the GNL_TARIH table using the string format '202512'.\n- The query limits results to 200 rows, though this may be redundant if the filter returns fewer than 200 rows.\n\noption_2:\nSQL: SELECT SUM(fpp.BRUT_PRIM_TL) AS prim_üretim_tutarı FROM AS_DWH.FACT_POL_POLICE_EK fpp JOIN AS_DWH.POL_POLICE_OZET ppo ON fpp.KAYNAK_SISTEM_ID = ppo.KAYNAK_SISTEM_ID AND fpp.POLICE_ID = ppo.POLICE_ID JOIN AS_DWH.GNL_TARIH gt ON ppo.ANA_POLICE_TANZIM_TARIH_ID = gt.TARIH_ID WHERE TO_CHAR(gt.TARIH) = '202512' FETCH FIRST 200 ROWS ONLY\nEXPLANATION: Question answered: What is the total production value (BRUT_PRIM_TL) for policies with an effective date in December 2025?\n\nTables used: AS_DWH.FACT_POL_POLICE_EK, AS_DWH.POL_POLICE_OZET, AS_DWH.GNL_TARIH\n\nFilters: Only records where the effective date (ANA_POLICE_TANZIM_TARIH_ID) is December 2025.\n\nGrouping/measures: Summing the BRUT_PRIM_TL column to calculate total production value.\n\nExpected output columns: prim_üretim_tutarı (total production value in Turkish Lira)\n\nAssumptions: \n- The query assumes that production is measured based on the effective date (ek tanzim tarihi) as per business rules.\n- The date filter is applied via the GNL_TARIH table using TARIH_ID.\n- The result is limited to 200 rows, though this may be redundant if the filter returns fewer than 200 records.\n\noption_3:\nSQL: SELECT SUM(fpp.BRUT_PRIM_TL) AS prim_üretim_tutarı FROM AS_DWH.FACT_POL_POLICE_EK fpp JOIN AS_DWH.POL_POLICE_OZET ppo ON fpp.KAYNAK_SISTEM_ID = ppo.KAYNAK_SISTEM_ID AND fpp.POLICE_ID = ppo.POLICE_ID WHERE TO_CHAR(ppo.TANZIM_TARIH_ID) = '202512' FETCH FIRST 200 ROWS ONLY\nEXPLANATION: Question answered: What is the total production value (BRUT_PRIM_TL) for policies with an additional policy date of December 2025?\n\nTables used: AS_DWH.FACT_POL_POLICE_EK, AS_DWH.POL_POLICE_OZET\n\nFilters: Only records where the additional policy date (TANZIM_TARIH_ID) is December 2025 (`TO_CHAR(ppo.TANZIM_TARIH_ID) = '202512'`).\n\nGrouping/measures: Summing the `BRUT_PRIM_TL` 