ma yapılmalı.\",\"Üretim raporlarında genel olarak geçen sene ile kıyaslama yapılır. Örneğin \\\"Geçen yıl ile cari yıl üretimimi karşılaştır.\\\" üretim tarafıyla ilgilenen kullanıcılar ve üst yönetim tarafından sık sorulur.\",\"En fazla üretim yapan 10 acenteyi / Akdeniz bölgesinde en fazla üretim yapan 10 acente / xxx no'lu acentenin en yüksek prime sahip ilk 10 müşterisini getir sık sorulan sorular arasındadır.\",\"Contains customer-identifying fields; apply least-privilege and masking in broad extracts.\",\"PII columns restricted: MUSTERI_ADI, MUSTERI_NUMARASI, MUSTERI_SOYADI\"],\"mandatory_rules\":[\"{'month': '202512'}\"],\"runtime_mandatory_rules\":[],\"retrieval_debug\":{\"selected_count\":20,\"total_documents\":20,\"effective_top_k\":500,\"min_score_threshold\":0.005,\"metadata_source\":\"C:\\\\Users\\\\ky4642\\\\talk-to-your-data-v0\\\\metadata\\\\agents\\\\metadata_vectored_uretim.json\"}}\n\nSQL_CANDIDATES:\noption_1:\nSQL: SELECT SUM(fpp.BRUT_PRIM_TL) AS prim_üretim_tutarı FROM AS_DWH.FACT_POL_POLICE_EK fpp JOIN AS_DWH.POL_POLICE_OZET ppo ON fpp.KAYNAK_SISTEM_ID = ppo.KAYNAK_SISTEM_ID AND fpp.POLICE_ID = ppo.POLICE_ID JOIN AS_DWH.GNL_TARIH gt ON ppo.TANZIM_TARIH_ID = gt.TARIH_ID WHERE TO_CHAR(gt.TARIH, 'YYYYMM') = '202512' FETCH FIRST 200 ROWS ONLY\nEXPLANATION: Question answered: What is the total production value (BRUT_PRIM_TL) for December 2025 based on the additional policy date?  \nTables used: AS_DWH.FACT_POL_POLICE_EK, AS_DWH.POL_POLICE_OZET, AS_DWH.GNL_TARIH  \nFilters: Only records where the additional policy date falls in December 2025 (`YYYYMM` format).  \nGrouping/measures: Summing the `BRUT_PRIM_TL` column to calculate total production value.  \nExpected output columns: `prim_üretim_tutarı` (total production value).  \nAssumptions: The query assumes that production reports are based on the additional policy date (`TANZIM_TARIH_ID`) and not the main policy start date. It also limits results to 200 rows, though no grouping is applied.\n\noption_2:\nSQL: SELECT SUM(fpp.BRUT_PRIM_TL) AS prim_üretim_tutarı FROM AS_DWH.FACT_POL_POLICE_EK fpp JOIN AS_DWH.POL_POLICE_OZET ppo ON fpp.KAYNAK_SISTEM_ID = ppo.KAYNAK_SISTEM_ID AND fpp.POLICE_ID = ppo.POLICE_ID JOIN AS_DWH.GNL_TARIH gt ON ppo.ANA_POLICE_TANZIM_TARIH_ID = gt.TARIH_ID WHERE TO_CHAR(gt.TARIH, 'YYYYMM') = '202512' FETCH FIRST 200 ROWS ONLY\nEXPLANATION: Question answered: What is the total production value (BRUT_PRIM_TL) for policies with an effective date in December 2025?\n\nTables used: AS_DWH.FACT_POL_POLICE_EK, AS_DWH.POL_POLICE_OZET, AS_DWH.GNL_TARIH\n\nFilters: Only records where the effective date (ANA_POLICE_TANZIM_TARIH) falls in December 2025 (`YYYYMM` format is '202512').\n\nGrouping/measures: Summing the `BRUT_PRIM_TL` column to calculate total production value.\n\nExpected output columns: `prim_üretim_tutarı` (total production value in Turkish Lira)\n\nAssumptions: \n- The query is intended for production reporting based on the effective date (`ANA_POLICE_TANZIM_TARIH`), as per business rules.\n- The `FETCH FIRST 200 ROWS ONLY` clause is likely a safeguard or testing limit, though it may not be necessary given the aggregation.\n- The join keys used are consistent with standard join definitions in the metadata.\n\noption_3:\nSQL: SELECT SUM(fpp.BRUT_PRIM_TL) AS prim_üretim_tutarı FROM AS_DWH.FACT_POL_POLICE_EK fpp JOIN AS_DWH.POL_POLICE_OZET ppo ON fpp.KAYNAK_SISTEM_ID = ppo.KAYNAK_SISTEM_ID AND fpp.POLICE_ID = ppo.POLICE_ID WHERE TO_CHAR(ppo.TANZIM_TARIH_ID, 'YYYYMM') = '202512' FETCH FIRST 200 ROWS ONLY\nEXPLANATION: Question answered: What is the total production value (BRUT_PRIM_TL) for policies with an effective date in December 2025?\n\nTables used: AS_DWH.FACT_POL_POLICE_EK, AS_DWH.POL_POLICE_OZET\n\nFilters: Only records where the effective date (TANZIM_TARIH_ID) falls in December 2025 (`YYYYMM` format is `'202512'`).\n\nGrouping/measures: Summing the `BRUT_PRIM_TL` column to calculate total production value.\n\nExpected output columns: `prim_üretim_tutarı` (total production value in Turkish Lira)\n\nAssumptions: \n- The join between `FACT_POL_POLICE_EK` and `POL_POLICE_OZET` is based on `KAYNAK_SISTEM_ID` and `POLICE_ID`, which are standard key-based joins.\n- The query is intended for production reporting and uses the effective date (`TANZIM_TARIH_ID`) as the basis for filtering, consistent with business rules.\n- The `FETCH FIRST 200 ROWS ONLY` clause is likely a safeguard or testing limit, though it may not be needed in production."}
