es.\n\noption_2:\nSQL: SELECT SUM(f.VOP_TL) AS total_production FROM AS_DWH.FACT_POL_POLICE_TEM_ASSET f JOIN AS_DWH.POL_POLICE_OZET o ON f.POLICE_ID = o.POLICE_ID AND f.KAYNAK_SISTEM_ID = o.KAYNAK_SISTEM_ID JOIN AS_DWH.GNL_TARIH t ON o.TANZIM_TARIH_ID = t.TARIH_ID WHERE TO_CHAR(t.TARIH, 'YYYY') = '2025' AND o.KAYNAK_SISTEM_ID = 'tanzimli' FETCH FIRST 200 ROWS ONLY\nEXPLANATION: Question answered: What was the total production (in TL) for policies sourced from the system \"tanzimli\" in the year 2025?  \nTables used: AS_DWH.FACT_POL_POLICE_TEM_ASSET, AS_DWH.POL_POLICE_OZET, AS_DWH.GNL_TARIH  \nFilters: Year is 2025, source system is \"tanzimli\"  \nGrouping/measures: Sum of VOP_TL (total production)  \nExpected output columns: total_production  \nAssumptions: VOP_TL represents production value in Turkish Lira (TL), and the query limits results to 200 rows (though only one row is expected due to aggregation).\n\noption_3:\nSQL: SELECT SUM(p.POLICE_SAYISI) * AVG(f.BRUT_PRIM_TL) AS total_production FROM AS_DWH.POLICE_SAYISI p JOIN AS_DWH.POL_POLICE_OZET o ON p.POLICE_ID = o.POLICE_ID JOIN AS_DWH.FACT_POL_POLICE_EK f ON o.POLICE_ID = f.POLICE_ID AND o.KAYNAK_SISTEM_ID = f.KAYNAK_SISTEM_ID JOIN AS_DWH.GNL_TARIH t ON o.TANZIM_TARIH_ID = t.TARIH_ID WHERE TO_CHAR(t.TARIH, 'YYYY') = '2025' AND o.KAYNAK_SISTEM_ID = 'tanzimli' FETCH FIRST 200 ROWS ONLY\nEXPLANATION: Question answered: What is the total production value (calculated as total police count multiplied by average gross premium) for policies sourced from the \"tanzimli\" system in the year 2025?\n\nTables used: AS_DWH.POLICE_SAYISI, AS_DWH.FACT_POL_POLICE_EK, AS_DWH.POL_POLICE_OZET, AS_DWH.GNL_TARIH\n\nFilters: \n- Policies with a source system ID of \"tanzimli\"\n- Policies with a date in the year 2025\n\nGrouping/measures: \n- Sum of police count (`POLICE_SAYISI`)\n- Average of gross premium (`BRUT_PRIM_TL`)\n- Multiplied together to calculate total production value\n\nExpected output columns: \n- `total_production`